		{"id":"label-compare","type":"text","text":"## 🆚 Compare with Tetris","x":350,"y":320,"width":220,"height":40,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"compare-detail","type":"text","text":"Same tech stack (raylib + C++).\nDifferent architectures:\n\n| Snake | Tetris |\n|-------|--------|\n| Scene polym. | Block inherit. |\n| Central state | Scattered state |\n| Edge-triggered | Instant response |\n| Procedural audio | Audio files |\n| `deque<Point>` | `int grid[][]` |\n\n→ Why? Different problems.","x":330,"y":380,"width":250,"height":240},"color":"5"},

		{"id":"learn-md","type":"file","file":"playground/snake/LEARN.md","x":-480,"y":500,"width":400,"height":60,"color":"2"}
